  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.0.0-rc02\" data-text=\"Version 1.0.0-rc02\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.0.0-rc02</h3>\n<p>July 14, 2021</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.compose.ui:ui-*:1.0.0-rc02</code> is released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/1a3ba62b97c98d85f6c0ac2fb6483fc9ac60872e..abcc318573114e39365e63de4bea7736a81491af/compose/ui\">Version 1.0.0-rc02 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Dialogs now follow the platform sizing behaviour. Set <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">usePlatformDefaultWidth</code> to false to override this behaviour. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/Iffaedb8890f59627a58fb4f33d06044ac120fd7d\">Iffaed</a>, <a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/192682388\">b/192682388</a>)</li>\n</ul>",
